It will look something like this:

        &lt;inSequence&gt;
          &lt;payloadFactory media-type=&quot;xml&quot;&gt;
                &lt;format&gt;
                &lt;test&gt;
                    &lt;ABC&gt;$1&lt;/ABC&gt;
                    &lt;XYZ&gt;$2&lt;/XYZ&gt;
                &lt;/test&gt;
                &lt;/format&gt;
                &lt;args&gt;
                    &lt;arg expression=&quot;//value[0]&quot;/&gt;
                    &lt;arg expression=&quot;//value[1]&quot;/&gt;
                &lt;/args&gt;
          &lt;/payloadFactory&gt;

